1.1.name: wordpress/ajax-search-lite
1.1.description:
A resonsive search engine, which will boost your user experience by providing a user friendly ajax powered search form. Very smooth animations with mobile device support. Boost the user experience by providing a powerful ajax search plugin to your visitors. It will rock!

Demo: http://wp-dreams.com/ajax-search-lite/

Like us on facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pages/WPDreams/383702515034741

Features List:

  • Search in posts and pages
  • Frontend search settings boxes
  • Images in search results
  • Fully ajax powered
  • Uses custom built jQuery for maximum compatibility
  • Caches images for faster response time

Homepage: wp-dreams.com
